	Lab4 SPOLKS
	Simple client-server app for file transmit via TCP
	+ announcing amount of transmitted/received data
	+ UDP protocol support
	- TCP support :)

Synopsis

Run as server:
$python main.py -s [-p port] [-f filename]

Run as client:
$python main.py -c [-a host] [-p port]

This time client must be run first.

Default host: 127.0.0.1
Default port: 12345
Client saves file with name 'rcvd.file'.
Default filename for server to send: 'send.file'.


